org.aludratest.service.gui.component

Interface GUIComponent

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Button, Checkbox, Dropdownbox, Element<E>, FileField, GenericElement, InputField, Label, Link, RadioButton, Window
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractElement, AbstractGUIComponent, ButtonImpl, CheckboxImpl, DropdownboxImpl, FileFieldImpl, GenericElementImpl, InputFieldImpl, LabelImpl, LinkImpl, RadioButtonImpl, WindowImpl

    public interface GUIComponent
    Parent interface for all Components of a Graphical User Interface, e.g. Elements or Windows.
    Author:
    Marcel Malitz, Volker Bergmann
